                    <h2 style="color: #00d9ff; font-size: 2.5em; margin-bottom: 20px; border: none;">SOC = Security Operations Center</h2>
                    <p style="font-size: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 0;">
                        A centralized unit that monitors, detects, analyzes, and responds to cybersecurity incidents
                    </p>
