                    </div>
                    <div style="background: #f8fafc; padding: 25px; border-radius: 10px; border-left: 5px solid #00d9ff; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                        <h4 style="color: #0a192f; font-size: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 10px;">üí∞ Reduced IT Costs</h4>
