                <p style="font-size: 1.4em; text-align: center; margin-top: 50px; padding: 30px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a192f 0%, #112240 100%); color: white; border-radius: 12px;">
                    <strong style="color: #00d9ff;">Key Concept:</strong> Federation doesn't store or sync passwords across systems. Instead, it establishes trust so one system can vouch for users authenticated by another system!
