                    <h3 style="color: #0a192f; font-size: 1.8em; margin-bottom: 20px;">‚úÖ Advantages</h3>
                    <div class="feature-grid">
                        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%); color: white; padding: 25px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.3);">
                            <h4 style="color: white; font-size: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 10px;">‚ö° Fast & Efficient</h4>
                            <p style="font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0;">
                                Computationally less intensive. Can encrypt large volumes of data quickly.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%); color: white; padding: 25px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.3);">
                            <h4 style="color: white; font-size: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 10px;">üí™ Strong Security</h4>
                            <p style="font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0;">
                                With sufficient key length (e.g., AES-256), virtually impossible to break with current technology.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%); color: white; padding: 25px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.3);">
                            <h4 style="color: white; font-size: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 10px;">üîã Low Resource Usage</h4>
                            <p style="font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0;">
                                Requires less computational power, suitable for devices with limited resources.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%); color: white; padding: 25px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.3);">
                            <h4 style="color: white; font-size: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 10px;">üì¶ Ideal for Bulk Data</h4>
                            <p style="font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0;">
                                Perfect for encrypting large files, databases, and disk encryption.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
