                        <h4 style="color: #dc3545; font-size: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 10px;">üéØ Vulnerable to Quantum Computing</h4>
                        <p style="font-size: 1.15em; color: #0a192f; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0;">
