                        <p style="font-size: 1.15em; color: #0a192f; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                            <strong>Modern, efficient alternative to RSA.</strong> Provides same security as RSA with much smaller key sizes. Increasingly popular for mobile/IoT due to efficiency.
                        </p>
