                            <p style="font-size: 1.1em; color: #0a192f; line-height: 1.8; margin: 0;">
                                Based on algebraic structure of elliptic curves over finite fields. Security relies on Elliptic Curve Discrete Logarithm Problem (ECDLP) - finding the scalar multiplier given two points on the curve.
                            </p>
