                                <strong>Key Sizes:</strong> 256-bit (standard), 384-bit, 521-bit<br>
                                <strong>Equivalent Security:</strong> ECC-256 ‚âà RSA-3072, ECC-384 ‚âà RSA-7680<br>
                                <strong>Speed:</strong> Faster than RSA (smaller keys = faster operations)<br>
                                <strong>Efficiency:</strong> Lower bandwidth, storage, computational requirements<br>
