                <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d9ff 0%, #0099cc 100%); color: white; padding: 35px; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 35px;">
                    <h3 style="color: white; font-size: 2em; margin-bottom: 25px; text-align: center;">ü§î Which One to Use?</h3>
                    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 25px;">
                        <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: 30px; border-radius: 12px;">
                            <h4 style="color: white; font-size: 1.6em; margin-bottom: 15px;">‚úÖ Use Symmetric When:</h4>
                            <ul style="font-size: 1.15em; line-height: 2; margin: 0;">
                                <li>Encrypting large files/databases</li>
                                <li>Disk/folder encryption</li>
                                <li>VPN tunnels (bulk data)</li>
                                <li>Performance is critical</li>
                                <li>Keys already securely shared</li>
                                <li>Single user/system (self-encryption)</li>
                            </ul>
