                        <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: 30px; border-radius: 12px;">
                            <h4 style="color: white; font-size: 1.6em; margin-bottom: 15px;">‚úÖ Use Asymmetric When:</h4>
                            <ul style="font-size: 1.15em; line-height: 2; margin: 0;">
                                <li>Establishing initial connection</li>
                                <li>Digital signatures needed</li>
